# Testing (pytest) — BillboardHub

- Deterministic tests: no real network unless explicitly marked integration.
- `backend/tests/conftest.py` sets isolated SQLite + `IMPORT_USE_LLM=false` for stable runs.
- Golden workbook test uses env `IMPORT_GOLDEN_WORKBOOK_PATH` only; never commit client filenames in tests.
- Arrange / Act / Assert; name tests after behavior.
- Assert outcomes (status codes, row counts), not private implementation details.

## Commands

```bash
cd backend && .venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/ -q
```
